Rapid prototype to make sure voice recognition was viable.
<br />
This prototype accept the different voice commands configured in the grammar files.<br />
It is able to control an instance of itunes (using the iTunesController library)  
<ul>
<li>play/pause</li>
<li>control volume (up, down, mute)</li>
<li>say what son by what artist is playing</li>
</ul>
<p>
It is also able to connect to yahoo weather and tell the current temperature as well as the condition (sunny, cloudy etc...)
</p>
